            <li>You smell burning or smoke</li>
            <li>You have elderly family members, infants, or pets at risk</li>
            <li>Temperatures are dangerously high</li>
            <li>The AC is making unusual loud noises</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Get Your AC Running Again</h2>
